<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Xudovand - choĘ»ponim mening,
 Men muhtojlik koĘ»rmayman aslo!
 U meni yam-yashil yaylovlarda yotqizar,
 Orombaxsh suvlar boĘ»ylab yetaklab borar.
 Jonimga U tetiklik kiritar,
 OĘ»z nomi uchun meni togĘ»ri yoĘ»lga boshlar!

[C1]
   /// Xudovand choĘ»ponim mening! ///
   Men muhtojlik koĘ»rmayman aslo!

[V2]
 OĘ»lim vodiysi zulmatida yursam ham,
 Dahshatlardan men qoĘ»rqmayman.
 Chunki Sen menga hamrohdirsan,
 OĘ»z hassangu xiviching
 Menga tassali berar!

[V3]
 Yovning koĘ»z oĘ»ngida
 Menga dasturxon tuzagansan,
 XushboĘ»y moy ila moylagansan boshimni,
 Lim - Lim toĘ»ldirgansan kosamni.
 Umrim boĘ»yi xayru inoyat izimdan yurar,
 Bor kunlarim Xudovandning uyida oĘ»tar</lyrics>
<title>Xudovand - ChoĘ»ponim Mening (anĘĽanaviy)</title>
</song>